//
// test/sema/width/repeat_expr.test — repeat-expression width fixture
// (T024 rollover; specs/006-m3-sema/tasks.md Phase 4a). Asserts the
// `RepeatExpr` for `4{0}` carries a `: BitVector(N)` Type suffix per
// `emit-ast-format.contract.md` Invariant 2 — the result width is
// `operand_width * repeat_count`.

// RUN: printf 'module m {\n  reg q = 4{0};\n}\n' > %t.nsl
// RUN: %nslc -emit=ast %t.nsl | FileCheck %s

// CHECK: (RegDecl {{.*}}name=q
// CHECK: (RepeatExpr {{.*}} : BitVector({{[0-9]+}})
